  "detailed_description": "<h1>INTRODUCING: MINIGOLF BLAST</h1><p></p><br><h1>JOIN THE DISCORD COMMUNITY</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/241240/extras/7f5dd41216f51c7ea313905e7084e7f8.poster.avif?t=1724702807\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/241240/extras/7f5dd41216f51c7ea313905e7084e7f8.webm?t=1724702807\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/241240/extras/7f5dd41216f51c7ea313905e7084e7f8.mp4?t=1724702807\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Play over 200 official puzzles and over 1,000 user created puzzles in the Workshop.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/241240/extras/4eacaf619a217bda8f743df18a054b30.poster.avif?t=1724702807\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/241240/extras/4eacaf619a217bda8f743df18a054b30.webm?t=1724702807\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/241240/extras/4eacaf619a217bda8f743df18a054b30.mp4?t=1724702807\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Use the many characters that interact in amusing ways.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/241240/extras/a70dcae53311588cd87b931ba3e1c606.poster.avif?t=1724702807\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/241240/extras/a70dcae53311588cd87b931ba3e1c606.webm?t=1724702807\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/241240/extras/a70dcae53311588cd87b931ba3e1c606.mp4?t=1724702807\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br>Play online to build contraptions together with up to 8 players in the Maker Lab.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/241240/extras/7fb19d2d8c75d152fcb7d90568d51a4b.poster.avif?t=1724702807\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/241240/extras/7fb19d2d8c75d152fcb7d90568d51a4b.webm?t=1724702807\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/241240/extras/7fb19d2d8c75d152fcb7d90568d51a4b.mp4?t=1724702807\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Make your own games with the built-in <strong>JavaScript Editor</strong> using Contraption Maker's physics and parts.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/241240/extras/929900e847eec40b3dbc021299057592.poster.avif?t=1724702807\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/241240/extras/929900e847eec40b3dbc021299057592.webm?t=1724702807\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/241240/extras/929900e847eec40b3dbc021299057592.mp4?t=1724702807\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Build your own ingenious contraptions and puzzles and share them.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/241240/extras/84e1f51c9701fa5d80d576d22512e326.poster.avif?t=1724702807\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/241240/extras/84e1f51c9701fa5d80d576d22512e326.webm?t=1724702807\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/241240/extras/84e1f51c9701fa5d80d576d22512e326.mp4?t=1724702807\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Create your own Cheese Factory or anything else that you can imagine.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/241240/extras/d347ace30d43d5781bd88e42050cefb3.poster.avif?t=1724702807\" width=600 height=364 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/241240/extras/d347ace30d43d5781bd88e42050cefb3.webm?t=1724702807\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/241240/extras/d347ace30d43d5781bd88e42050cefb3.mp4?t=1724702807\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>You can make large elaborate endless machines.",
